{{#> layout }}
  <div class="bg-warning">
    <div class="container py-4">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h1>Slider Component</h1>
          <p>Compare two images. Before and after.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <style>
            .styled {
              transition: box-shadow 200ms ease-in-out;
            }

            .styled:focus {
              outline: none;
              box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px 5px rgba(57, 57, 57, 0.28);
            }
          </style>
          <img-comparison-slider class="styled">
            <img
              slot="first"
              width="100%"
              src="images/sunflowers.webp"
            />
            <img
              slot="second"
              width="100%"
              src="images/sunflowers-blurred.webp"
            />
          </img-comparison-slider>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container mt-3">
    <h1 class="my-5">Reasons to use img-comparison-slider</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <p>
          This <a href="https://github.com/sneas/img-comparison-slider/blob/master/LICENSE">free open source</a> slider
          component has been created to demonstrate the difference between two images. For example, for showing the
          difference before and after applying photo effects or filters, comparing photos of rooms before and after
          construction, or revealing landscape changes within time. The most pleasant user experience with the component
          could be achieved by comparing images with pixel-perfectly fit fragments. This component is well-suited for
          news portals, artist or design portfolios.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-5">
          Because this is a Web Component, it could be effortlessly added to almost any web application or design
          system. The component provides wide range of settings &ndash; a lot of configuration ideas and styling
          techniques could be found in the <a href="/examples.html">Examples</a>. The setup and settings documentation
          is available on the <a href="https://github.com/sneas/img-comparison-slider">components GitHub page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <h3 class="mb-5">Component Features</h3>

        <div class="row align-items-center gy-5 mb-5">
          {{#each features}}
            <div class="col-2 col-lg-1 text-center">
              <i class="{{ this.icon }} fa-3x"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 col-lg-3">
              {{ this.title }}
            </div>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{{/layout}}
